Provides: ollmcp
Description: MCP Client for Ollama
 MCP Client for Ollama (ollmcp) is a modern, interactive terminal
 application for connecting local Ollama LLMs to one or more Model
 Context Protocol (MCP) servers, enabling advanced tool use and
 workflow automation.
 .
 Features include multi-server support, MCP prompts, agent mode,
 human-in-the-loop tool execution, advanced model configuration,
 fuzzy autocomplete, performance metrics, and streaming responses.
